librgs
------------------------------------------
Retro game engine

Runtime requirements:
  cygwin-1.7.35-1
  librgs0-0.9.0+git20120424-1bl1
  libSDL1.2_0-1.2.15-2

Build requirements:
(besides corresponding -devel packages)
  binutils-2.25-1
  cmake-3.1.2-1
  cygport-0.18.1-1
  gcc-core-4.9.2-3
  gcc-objc-4.9.2-3
  make-4.1-1

Canonical website:
  https://github.com/ivansafrin/librgs

Canonical download:
  https://github.com/ivansafrin/librgs.git

-------------------------------------------

Build instructions:
  1. unpack librgs-0.9.0+git20120424-X-src.tar.xz
  2. if you use setup to install this src package,
     it will be unpacked under /usr/src automatically
        % cd /usr/src
        % cygport ./librgs-0.9.0+git20120424-X.cygport all

This will create:
  /usr/src/librgs-0.9.0+git20120424-X-src.tar.xz
  /usr/src/librgs-0.9.0+git20120424-X.tar.xz
  /usr/src/librgs0-0.9.0+git20120424-X.tar.xz
  /usr/src/librgs-devel-0.9.0+git20120424-X.tar.xz

-------------------------------------------

Files included in the binary package:

(librgs)
  /usr/share/doc/Cygwin/librgs.README
  /usr/share/doc/LICENSE.txt
  /usr/share/doc/librgs/LICENSE.txt
  /usr/share/doc/librgs/README.txt

(librgs0)
  /usr/bin/cygrgs-0.dll

(librgs-devel)
  /usr/include/librgs/BFont.h
